#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:647
msgid "Over Limit"
msgstr "Przekroczenie limitu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:269
msgid "What is the Army Body Fat Calculator?"
msgstr "Czym jest kalkulator tkanki tłuszczowej dla armii?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:271
msgid ""
"The US Army Body Fat Calculator uses a specific measurement-based formula to"
" estimate body fat percentage. This method is used by the US Army to "
"determine if service members meet body composition standards required for "
"military service."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator tkanki tłuszczowej armii amerykańskiej wykorzystuje specjalny "
"wzór oparty na pomiarach do oszacowania procentowej zawartości tkanki "
"tłuszczowej. Ta metoda jest stosowana przez armię amerykańską w celu "
"ustalenia, czy żołnierze spełniają standardy składu ciała wymagane do służby"
" wojskowej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Unlike BMI, this calculator uses actual body measurements (neck, waist, and "
"hip circumference) along with height to provide a more accurate assessment "
"of body fat percentage."
msgstr ""
"W przeciwieństwie do BMI, kalkulator ten wykorzystuje rzeczywiste wymiary "
"ciała (obwód szyi, talii i bioder) wraz ze wzrostem, aby zapewnić "
"dokładniejszą ocenę procentowej zawartości tkanki tłuszczowej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:283
msgid "Males"
msgstr "Mężczyźni"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:285
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Ages 17-20: Max 20%% | Ages 21-27: Max 22%% | Ages 28-39: Max 24%% | Ages "
"40+: Max 26%%"
msgstr ""
"Wiek 17-20: Maks. 20%% | Wiek 21-27: Maks. 22%% | Wiek 28-39: Maks. 24%% | "
"Wiek 40+: Maks. 26%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:289
msgid "Females"
msgstr "Kobiety"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:291
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Ages 17-20: Max 30%% | Ages 21-27: Max 32%% | Ages 28-39: Max 34%% | Ages "
"40+: Max 36%%"
msgstr ""
"Wiek 17-20: Maks. 30%% | Wiek 21-27: Maks. 32%% | Wiek 28-39: Maks. 34%% | "
"Wiek 40+: Maks. 36%%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:301
msgid "Select your gender (Male or Female)"
msgstr "Wybierz swoją płeć (mężczyzna lub kobieta)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:302
msgid "Enter your age (17-65 years)"
msgstr "Podaj swój wiek (17-65 lat)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:303
msgid "Enter your height in inches"
msgstr "Podaj swój wzrost w calach"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:304
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:440
msgid "Measure and enter your neck circumference (just below the larynx)"
msgstr "Zmierz i podaj obwód szyi (tuż pod krtani)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:305
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:441
msgid "Measure and enter your waist circumference (at the navel level)"
msgstr "Zmierz i podaj obwód talii (na poziomie pępka)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:306
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:442
msgid "For females, measure and enter your hip circumference (widest point)"
msgstr ""
"W przypadku kobiet zmierz i wprowadź obwód bioder (w najszerszym miejscu)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:307
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:443
msgid "Click 'Calculate Body Fat' to see your results"
msgstr "Kliknij „Oblicz zawartość tkanki tłuszczowej”, aby zobaczyć wyniki"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:313
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:450
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:365
msgid "How to Take Measurements"
msgstr "Jak dokonywać pomiarów"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:316
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:453
msgid "Neck Measurement"
msgstr "Pomiar szyi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Measure around the neck, just below the larynx (Adam's apple). Keep the tape"
" measure horizontal and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Zmierz obwód szyi, tuż pod krtani (jabłko Adama). Trzymaj miarkę poziomo i "
"dobrze dopasowaną, ale nie ciasną."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:322
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:459
msgid "Waist Measurement"
msgstr "Pomiar talii"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"Measure at the navel level (belly button), not at the narrowest point. Stand"
" straight, breathe normally, and measure at the end of a normal breath."
msgstr ""
"Mierz na poziomie pępka (pępka), a nie w najwęższym miejscu. Stań prosto, "
"oddychaj normalnie i mierz na końcu normalnego oddechu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:328
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:465
msgid "Hip Measurement (Females Only)"
msgstr "Pomiar bioder (tylko kobiety)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"Measure around the hips at the widest point. This is typically around the "
"buttocks area. Keep the tape measure horizontal."
msgstr ""
"Zmierz obwód bioder w najszerszym miejscu. Zwykle dzieje się to w okolicy "
"pośladków. Trzymaj miarkę poziomo."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Your calculated body fat percentage based on the US Army formula. This is an"
" estimate and may vary from other measurement methods."
msgstr ""
"Obliczona zawartość tkanki tłuszczowej w organizmie na podstawie wzoru armii"
" amerykańskiej. Jest to wartość szacunkowa i może różnić się od innych metod"
" pomiaru."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:347
msgid "Maximum Allowed"
msgstr "Maksymalnie dozwolone"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:349
msgid ""
"The maximum body fat percentage allowed for your age and gender according to"
" US Army standards. If your percentage is below this, you pass."
msgstr ""
"Maksymalna zawartość tkanki tłuszczowej dozwolona dla Twojego wieku i płci, "
"zgodnie ze standardami armii amerykańskiej. Jeśli Twój procent jest niższy, "
"zdajesz."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:353
msgid "Pass/Fail Status"
msgstr "Stan pozytywny/negatywny"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:355
msgid ""
"Indicates whether you meet the Army body fat standards. 'Pass' means you're "
"within the allowed range, 'Fail' means you exceed it."
msgstr ""
"Wskazuje, czy spełniasz standardy dotyczące tkanki tłuszczowej obowiązujące "
"w armii. „Pass” oznacza, że ​​mieścisz się w dozwolonym zakresie, „Fail” "
"oznacza, że ​​go przekroczyłeś."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:361
msgid ""
"The difference between your body fat percentage and the maximum allowed. "
"Positive values mean you're over the limit, negative values mean you're "
"under."
msgstr ""
"Różnica między procentową zawartością tkanki tłuszczowej w organizmie a "
"maksymalną dozwoloną zawartością. Wartości dodatnie oznaczają, że "
"przekroczyłeś limit, wartości ujemne oznaczają, że jesteś poniżej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:372
msgid "Body Fat Gauge Chart"
msgstr "Wykres wskaźnika tkanki tłuszczowej"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"A circular gauge showing your body fat percentage visually. The color "
"corresponds to your status (green for pass, yellow/orange/red for fail)."
msgstr ""
"Okrągły wskaźnik pokazujący wizualnie procent tkanki tłuszczowej. Kolor "
"odpowiada Twojemu statusowi (zielony – pozytywny, "
"żółty/pomarańczowy/czerwony – niezaliczony)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:378
msgid "Army Standards Chart"
msgstr "Wykres standardów armii"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:380
msgid ""
"Shows different body fat ranges (Excellent, Good, Acceptable, Over Limit). "
"Your current percentage is highlighted in the appropriate range."
msgstr ""
"Pokazuje różne zakresy tkanki tłuszczowej (doskonałe, dobre, akceptowalne, "
"powyżej limitu). Twój aktualny procent jest podświetlony w odpowiednim "
"zakresie."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:384
msgid "Comparison Chart"
msgstr "Tabela porównawcza"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"A direct comparison between your body fat percentage and the maximum allowed"
" for your age and gender group."
msgstr ""
"Bezpośrednie porównanie procentowej zawartości tkanki tłuszczowej w "
"organizmie z maksymalną dozwoloną dla Twojej grupy wiekowej i płci."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"A visual scale showing body fat ranges with a marker indicating your current"
" position relative to Army standards."
msgstr ""
"Skala wizualna pokazująca zakresy tkanki tłuszczowej ze znacznikiem "
"wskazującym Twoją aktualną pozycję w stosunku do standardów wojskowych."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:400
msgid "US Army Body Fat Formula"
msgstr "Formuła tłuszczu w organizmie armii amerykańskiej"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:403
msgid "For Males:"
msgstr "Dla mężczyzn:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:404
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Body Fat %% = 86.010 × log10(waist - neck) - 70.041 × log10(height) + 36.76"
msgstr ""
"Tkanka tłuszczowa %% = 86,010 × log10 (talia - szyja) - 70,041 × log10 "
"(wzrost) + 36,76"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:407
msgid "For Females:"
msgstr "Dla kobiet:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:408
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Body Fat %% = 163.205 × log10(waist + hip - neck) - 97.684 × log10(height) -"
" 78.387"
msgstr ""
"Tkanka tłuszczowa %% = 163,205 × log10 (talia + biodra - szyja) - 97,684 × "
"log10 (wzrost) - 78,387"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:411
msgid ""
"All measurements are in inches. The formula uses logarithmic calculations to"
" estimate body fat percentage based on body circumference measurements."
msgstr ""
"Wszystkie pomiary podano w calach. Formuła wykorzystuje obliczenia "
"logarytmiczne do oszacowania procentowej zawartości tkanki tłuszczowej na "
"podstawie pomiarów obwodu ciała."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:424
msgid ""
"This calculator uses the US Army body fat estimation formula. Actual body "
"fat percentage may vary when measured with more precise methods like DEXA "
"scan or hydrostatic weighing."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ten korzysta ze wzoru służącego do szacowania zawartości tkanki "
"tłuszczowej w organizmie armii amerykańskiej. Rzeczywisty procent tkanki "
"tłuszczowej może się różnić w przypadku pomiaru bardziej precyzyjnymi "
"metodami, takimi jak skan DEXA lub ważenie hydrostatyczne."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:430
msgid ""
"Accurate measurements are crucial. Measure at the same time of day, "
"preferably in the morning before eating."
msgstr ""
"Dokładne pomiary są kluczowe. Pomiar należy wykonywać o tej samej porze "
"dnia, najlepiej rano przed jedzeniem."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Official"
" Army body fat assessments are conducted by trained personnel using "
"standardized procedures."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ten służy wyłącznie celom edukacyjnym i informacyjnym. Oficjalne "
"oceny tkanki tłuszczowej w organizmie armii przeprowadzane są przez "
"przeszkolony personel przy użyciu standardowych procedur."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:442
msgid ""
"Body fat standards may change. Always refer to the latest official US Army "
"regulations for current requirements."
msgstr ""
"Standardy zawartości tkanki tłuszczowej mogą ulec zmianie. Aby zapoznać się "
"z aktualnymi wymaganiami, należy zawsze zapoznać się z najnowszymi "
"oficjalnymi przepisami armii amerykańskiej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:449
msgid "Tips for Meeting Army Standards"
msgstr "Wskazówki dotyczące spełnienia standardów wojskowych"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:451
msgid "If you're over the body fat limit, consider:"
msgstr "Jeśli przekroczyłeś limit tkanki tłuszczowej, rozważ:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:453
msgid "Regular cardiovascular exercise (running, cycling, swimming)"
msgstr ""
"Regularne ćwiczenia sercowo-naczyniowe (bieganie, jazda na rowerze, "
"pływanie)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:454
msgid "Strength training to build lean muscle mass"
msgstr "Trening siłowy w celu budowy beztłuszczowej masy mięśniowej"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:455
msgid "A balanced diet with appropriate calorie intake"
msgstr "Zbilansowana dieta z odpowiednią podażą kalorii"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:456
msgid "Consistent sleep schedule and stress management"
msgstr "Spójny harmonogram snu i radzenie sobie ze stresem"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:457
msgid "Consulting with a healthcare provider or fitness professional"
msgstr "Konsultacja z lekarzem lub specjalistą fitness"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:14
