msgid "What is Conception?"
msgstr "Co to jest poczęcie?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:286
msgid ""
"Conception occurs when a sperm fertilizes an egg, typically happening during"
" ovulation. This is the moment when pregnancy begins, and it usually occurs "
"about 14 days after the start of your last menstrual period (LMP) in a "
"28-day cycle."
msgstr ""
"Do poczęcia dochodzi, gdy plemnik zapładnia komórkę jajową, co zwykle ma "
"miejsce podczas owulacji. Jest to moment, w którym rozpoczyna się ciąża i "
"zwykle następuje około 14 dni po rozpoczęciu ostatniej miesiączki (LMP) w "
"28-dniowym cyklu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:289
msgid ""
"The conception date is important for tracking fetal development, "
"understanding pregnancy milestones, and calculating your due date. However, "
"it's important to note that the exact moment of conception is difficult to "
"determine precisely."
msgstr ""
"Data poczęcia jest ważna dla śledzenia rozwoju płodu, zrozumienia kamieni "
"milowych ciąży i obliczenia terminu porodu. Należy jednak pamiętać, że "
"dokładny moment poczęcia jest trudny do dokładnego określenia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:295
msgid "How Conception Date is Calculated"
msgstr "Jak obliczana jest data poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:300
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs approximately 266 days (38 weeks) before the due"
" date. This is calculated by subtracting 266 days from your expected due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Do poczęcia dochodzi zwykle około 266 dni (38 tygodni) przed terminem "
"porodu. Oblicza się to poprzez odjęcie 266 dni od oczekiwanego terminu "
"płatności."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:302
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Due Date - 266 days"
msgstr "Wzór: Data poczęcia = Termin porodu – 266 dni"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:305
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:77
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:81
msgid "From Last Menstrual Period"
msgstr "Z ostatniej miesiączki"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:307
msgid ""
"Conception typically occurs around 14 days before your next expected period."
" For a 28-day cycle, this is 14 days after the first day of your last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Poczęcie następuje zazwyczaj około 14 dni przed następną spodziewaną "
"miesiączką. W przypadku cyklu 28-dniowego jest to 14 dni od pierwszego dnia "
"ostatniej miesiączki."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:309
msgid "Formula: Conception Date = Last Period + (Cycle Length - 14 days)"
msgstr "Wzór: Data poczęcia = Ostatni okres + (Długość cyklu – 14 dni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:318
msgid "Choose your calculation method: From Due Date or From Last Period"
msgstr "Wybierz metodę obliczeń: Z terminu płatności lub Z ostatniego okresu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:319
msgid "If using due date method, enter your expected due date"
msgstr "Jeśli używasz metody terminu, wprowadź oczekiwany termin"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"If using last period method, enter the first day of your last menstrual "
"period and your cycle length (default: 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Jeśli używasz metody ostatniej miesiączki, wprowadź pierwszy dzień ostatniej"
" miesiączki i długość cyklu (domyślnie: 28 dni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:321
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:341
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:373
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see your results"
msgstr "Kliknij „Oblicz”, aby zobaczyć wyniki"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Review your conception date, pregnancy timeline, and trimester information"
msgstr "Przejrzyj datę poczęcia, harmonogram ciąży i informacje o trymestrze"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:323
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:343
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:365
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your pregnancy progress"
msgstr "Skorzystaj z wykresów, aby zwizualizować postęp ciąży"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:334
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception likely occurred. This is typically within"
" a 5-6 day window around ovulation when the egg is viable for fertilization."
msgstr ""
"Szacowana data prawdopodobnego wystąpienia poczęcia. Zwykle ma to miejsce w "
"ciągu 5-6 dni około owulacji, kiedy komórka jajowa jest zdolna do "
"zapłodnienia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:338
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:364
msgid "Last Menstrual Period (LMP)"
msgstr "Ostatnia miesiączka (LMP)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"The first day of your last menstrual period. This is used as the starting "
"point for calculating pregnancy weeks and due date."
msgstr ""
"Pierwszy dzień ostatniej miesiączki. Jest to punkt wyjścia do obliczenia "
"tygodni ciąży i terminu porodu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:346
msgid ""
"The estimated date when your baby is due. This is calculated as 280 days (40"
" weeks) from the first day of your last menstrual period."
msgstr ""
"Przewidywana data porodu. Oblicza się go jako 280 dni (40 tygodni) od "
"pierwszego dnia ostatniej miesiączki."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:350
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:370
msgid "Weeks and Days Pregnant"
msgstr "Tygodnie i dni ciąży"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:352
msgid ""
"The number of weeks and days since your last menstrual period. Pregnancy is "
"typically counted from the LMP, not from conception."
msgstr ""
"Liczba tygodni i dni od ostatniej miesiączki. Ciążę zazwyczaj liczy się od "
"LMP, a nie od poczęcia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:358
msgid ""
"Your current trimester: First (weeks 1-13), Second (weeks 14-27), or Third "
"(weeks 28-40). Each trimester has different developmental milestones."
msgstr ""
"Twój obecny trymestr: pierwszy (tygodnie 1-13), drugi (tygodnie 14-27) lub "
"trzeci (tygodnie 28-40). Każdy trymestr ma inne kamienie milowe w rozwoju."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:382
msgid "Progress Percentage"
msgstr "Procent postępu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"The percentage of your pregnancy completed based on a full 40-week (280-day)"
" pregnancy term."
msgstr ""
"Odsetek zakończonej ciąży w oparciu o pełny okres ciąży trwający 40 tygodni "
"(280 dni)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:372
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:333
msgid "Pregnancy Trimesters"
msgstr "Trymestry ciąży"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:375
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:450
msgid "First Trimester (Weeks 1-13)"
msgstr "Pierwszy trymestr (tygodnie 1-13)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Early development, organ formation, and initial fetal growth. Many women "
"experience morning sickness and fatigue during this period."
msgstr ""
"Wczesny rozwój, tworzenie narządów i początkowy wzrost płodu. W tym okresie "
"wiele kobiet doświadcza porannych mdłości i zmęczenia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Heartbeat begins, major organs form, baby's sex is "
"determined"
msgstr ""
"Kluczowe kamienie milowe: rozpoczyna się bicie serca, powstają główne "
"narządy, określana jest płeć dziecka"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:382
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 14-27)"
msgstr "Drugi trymestr (tygodnie 14-27)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"Rapid growth, movement felt, and visible baby bump. Often called the "
"'honeymoon period' of pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Szybki wzrost, wyczuwalne ruchy i widoczny brzuszek. Często nazywany "
"„okresem miodowym” ciąży."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby movements felt, anatomy scan, baby can hear sounds"
msgstr ""
"Kluczowe kamienie milowe: Wyczucie ruchów dziecka, skanowanie anatomii, "
"dziecko słyszy dźwięki"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:389
msgid "Third Trimester (Weeks 28-40)"
msgstr "Trzeci trymestr (tygodnie 28-40)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"Final growth phase, preparation for birth, and increased discomfort. Baby "
"gains most weight during this period."
msgstr ""
"Końcowa faza wzrostu, przygotowanie do porodu i zwiększony dyskomfort. W tym"
" okresie dziecko przybiera na wadze najwięcej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Key milestones: Baby reaches full term (37 weeks), lungs mature, ready for "
"birth"
msgstr ""
"Kluczowe kamienie milowe: Dziecko osiąga pełny termin (37 tygodni), płuca "
"dojrzewają, są gotowe do porodu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:400
msgid "Understanding the Conception Window"
msgstr "Zrozumienie okna poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:402
msgid "Conception can occur within a 5-6 day window around ovulation:"
msgstr "Poczęcie może nastąpić w ciągu 5-6 dni około owulacji:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:405
msgid "Sperm can survive in the female reproductive tract for up to 5 days"
msgstr "Plemnik może przetrwać w drogach rodnych kobiety do 5 dni"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"The egg is viable for fertilization for about 12-24 hours after ovulation"
msgstr ""
"Jajo jest zdolne do zapłodnienia przez około 12–24 godziny po owulacji"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"The most fertile window is typically 2-3 days before ovulation and the day "
"of ovulation"
msgstr ""
"Najbardziej płodne okno to zazwyczaj 2-3 dni przed owulacją i dzień owulacji"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:408
msgid ""
"The calculator provides an estimated conception date, but actual conception "
"may have occurred within a few days of this date"
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator podaje szacunkową datę poczęcia, ale rzeczywiste poczęcie może "
"nastąpić w ciągu kilku dni od tej daty"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:420
msgid ""
"Conception dates are estimates. The exact moment of conception is difficult "
"to determine, and actual conception may have occurred within a 5-6 day "
"window around the calculated date."
msgstr ""
"Daty poczęcia są szacunkowe. Dokładny moment poczęcia jest trudny do "
"ustalenia, a rzeczywiste poczęcie może nastąpić w ciągu 5–6 dni od "
"obliczonej daty."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is typically counted from the first day of your last menstrual "
"period (LMP), not from conception. This is why pregnancy is said to last 40 "
"weeks even though conception occurs about 2 weeks after LMP."
msgstr ""
"Ciążę zazwyczaj liczy się od pierwszego dnia ostatniej miesiączki (LMP), a "
"nie od poczęcia. Dlatego mówi się, że ciąża trwa 40 tygodni, mimo że "
"poczęcie następuje około 2 tygodnie po LMP."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Individual cycle lengths vary. If your cycle is longer or shorter than 28 "
"days, adjust the cycle length in the calculator for more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"Poszczególne długości cykli są różne. Jeśli Twój cykl jest dłuższy lub "
"krótszy niż 28 dni, dostosuj długość cyklu w kalkulatorze, aby uzyskać "
"dokładniejsze wyniki."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:438
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with healthcare providers for accurate pregnancy dating, especially "
"for medical decisions and prenatal care."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ten służy wyłącznie celom edukacyjnym i informacyjnym. Zawsze "
"konsultuj się z podmiotami świadczącymi opiekę zdrowotną w celu uzyskania "
"dokładnego datowania ciąży, szczególnie w przypadku decyzji medycznych i "
"opieki prenatalnej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:522
msgid "Please enter a due date."
msgstr "Proszę wprowadzić termin."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:533
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:550
msgid "Please enter your last menstrual period date."
msgstr "Proszę podać datę ostatniej miesiączki."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/conception_calculator.html:789
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:845
msgid "Completed"
msgstr "Zakończony"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:44
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:56
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:45
msgid "Due Date Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator terminu płatności"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:4
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Pregnancy Due Date"
msgstr "Oblicz termin porodu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate your pregnancy due date based on last menstrual period or "
"conception date. Free due date calculator with trimester tracking."
msgstr ""
"Oblicz termin porodu na podstawie ostatniej miesiączki lub daty poczęcia. "
"Bezpłatny kalkulator terminu porodu ze śledzeniem trymestru."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"due date calculator, pregnancy due date, due date, pregnancy calculator, "
"trimester calculator"
msgstr ""
"kalkulator terminu porodu, termin porodu, termin porodu, kalkulator ciąży, "
"kalkulator trymestru"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:15
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:59
msgid ""
"Calculate your pregnancy due date based on last menstrual period or "
"conception date."
msgstr ""
"Oblicz termin porodu na podstawie ostatniej miesiączki lub daty poczęcia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:73
msgid "Calculate Due Date"
msgstr "Oblicz termin płatności"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:85
msgid "From Last Menstrual Period (LMP)"
msgstr "Z ostatniej miesiączki (LMP)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:325
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:81
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:85
msgid "From Conception Date"
msgstr "Od daty poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:109
msgid "Estimated date of conception"
msgstr "Szacowana data poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:152
msgid ""
"Enter your information to calculate your due date and pregnancy timeline "
"with detailed analysis and charts."
msgstr ""
"Wprowadź swoje dane, aby obliczyć termin porodu i harmonogram ciąży ze "
"szczegółową analizą i wykresami."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:285
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:392
msgid "Pregnancy Milestones"
msgstr "Kamienie milowe ciąży"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:304
msgid "What is a Due Date?"
msgstr "Co to jest termin?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"A due date (also called expected date of delivery or EDD) is the estimated "
"date when a pregnant woman is most likely to give birth. It's calculated as "
"40 weeks (280 days) from the first day of the last menstrual period (LMP)."
msgstr ""
"Termin porodu (zwany także oczekiwaną datą porodu lub EDD) to szacunkowa "
"data, w której kobieta w ciąży z największym prawdopodobieństwem urodzi. "
"Oblicza się go jako 40 tygodni (280 dni) od pierwszego dnia ostatniej "
"miesiączki (LMP)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:309
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The due date is an estimate, not an exact date. Only about 5%% of babies are"
" born exactly on their due date, with most babies born within two weeks "
"before or after the due date."
msgstr ""
"Termin płatności jest szacunkowy, a nie dokładny. Tylko około 5%% dzieci "
"rodzi się dokładnie w terminie, a większość dzieci rodzi się w ciągu dwóch "
"tygodni przed terminem porodu lub po nim."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:315
msgid "How Due Date is Calculated"
msgstr "Jak obliczany jest termin płatności"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:318
msgid "Naegele's Rule (From LMP)"
msgstr "Reguła Naegelego (z LMP)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"The most common method: Add 1 year, subtract 3 months, and add 7 days to the"
" first day of your last menstrual period. Simplified: Add 280 days (40 "
"weeks) to LMP."
msgstr ""
"Najpopularniejsza metoda: dodaj 1 rok, odejmij 3 miesiące i dodaj 7 dni do "
"pierwszego dnia ostatniej miesiączki. Uproszczone: dodaj 280 dni (40 "
"tygodni) do LMP."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:322
msgid "Formula: Due Date = LMP + 280 days"
msgstr "Wzór: Termin płatności = LMP + 280 dni"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"If you know the conception date, add 266 days (38 weeks) to calculate the "
"due date. This accounts for the typical 2-week period between LMP and "
"conception."
msgstr ""
"Jeśli znasz datę poczęcia, dodaj 266 dni (38 tygodni), aby obliczyć termin "
"porodu. Stanowi to typowy 2-tygodniowy okres między LMP a poczęciem."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:329
msgid "Formula: Due Date = Conception Date + 266 days"
msgstr "Wzór: Termin porodu = Data poczęcia + 266 dni"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Last Menstrual Period or From "
"Conception Date"
msgstr "Wybierz metodę obliczeń: od ostatniej miesiączki lub od daty poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:339
msgid ""
"If using LMP method, enter the first day of your last menstrual period and "
"your cycle length (default: 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Jeśli używasz metody LMP, wpisz pierwszy dzień ostatniej miesiączki i "
"długość cyklu (domyślnie: 28 dni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"If using conception date method, enter the estimated date of conception"
msgstr "Jeśli używasz metody daty poczęcia, wprowadź szacunkową datę poczęcia"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Review your due date, pregnancy timeline, trimester information, and "
"milestones"
msgstr ""
"Przejrzyj termin porodu, harmonogram ciąży, informacje o trymestrze i "
"kamienie milowe"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"The estimated date when your baby is due. This is calculated as 280 days (40"
" weeks) from your last menstrual period or 266 days from conception."
msgstr ""
"Przewidywana data porodu. Oblicza się go jako 280 dni (40 tygodni) od "
"ostatniej miesiączki lub 266 dni od poczęcia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception likely occurred. This is typically 14 "
"days after the first day of your last period (or cycle_length - 14 days for "
"variable cycles)."
msgstr ""
"Szacowana data prawdopodobnego wystąpienia poczęcia. Zwykle jest to 14 dni "
"po pierwszym dniu ostatniej miesiączki (lub długość_cyklu – 14 dni w "
"przypadku cykli zmiennych)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"The first day of your last menstrual period. This is the standard starting "
"point for calculating pregnancy weeks and due date."
msgstr ""
"Pierwszy dzień ostatniej miesiączki. Jest to standardowy punkt wyjścia do "
"obliczania tygodni ciąży i terminu porodu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:372
msgid ""
"The number of weeks and days since your last menstrual period. Pregnancy is "
"counted from LMP, not from conception."
msgstr ""
"Liczba tygodni i dni od ostatniej miesiączki. Ciążę liczy się od LMP, a nie "
"od poczęcia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:378
msgid ""
"Your current trimester: First (weeks 1-13), Second (weeks 14-27), or Third "
"(weeks 28-40)."
msgstr ""
"Twój obecny trymestr: pierwszy (tygodnie 1-13), drugi (tygodnie 14-27) lub "
"trzeci (tygodnie 28-40)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"The percentage of your pregnancy completed based on a full 40-week (280-day)"
" term."
msgstr ""
"Odsetek zakończonej ciąży w oparciu o pełny okres 40 tygodni (280 dni)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:395
msgid "First Trimester End (13 weeks)"
msgstr "Koniec pierwszego trymestru (13 tygodni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"End of the first trimester. Major organ development is complete, and the "
"risk of miscarriage decreases significantly."
msgstr ""
"Koniec pierwszego trymestru. Zakończono rozwój głównych narządów, a ryzyko "
"poronienia znacznie maleje."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:401
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:675
msgid "Viability Week (24 weeks)"
msgstr "Tydzień żywotności (24 tygodnie)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"The point at which a baby has a chance of survival outside the womb with "
"medical intervention."
msgstr ""
"Moment, w którym dziecko ma szansę na przeżycie poza macicą, pod warunkiem "
"interwencji medycznej."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:407
msgid "Second Trimester End (27 weeks)"
msgstr "Koniec drugiego trymestru (27 tygodni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"End of the second trimester. Baby's movements are strong, and most major "
"development is complete."
msgstr ""
"Koniec drugiego trymestru. Ruchy dziecka są silne, a większość "
"najważniejszych procesów rozwojowych jest zakończona."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:413
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:677
msgid "Full Term (37 weeks)"
msgstr "Pełny semestr (37 tygodni)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"Baby is considered full-term and ready for birth. Lungs and other organs are"
" mature."
msgstr ""
"Dziecko uważa się za donoszone i gotowe do porodu. Płuca i inne narządy są "
"dojrzałe."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:423
msgid "Due Date Accuracy"
msgstr "Dokładność terminu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates, not exact dates. Several factors can affect the "
"accuracy:"
msgstr ""
"Terminy płatności są szacunkowe, a nie dokładne. Na dokładność może wpływać "
"kilka czynników:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:428
msgid "Irregular menstrual cycles"
msgstr "Nieregularne cykle menstruacyjne"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:429
msgid "Uncertainty about the exact date of LMP"
msgstr "Niepewność co do dokładnej daty LMP"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:430
msgid "Variations in the length of pregnancy (normal range: 37-42 weeks)"
msgstr "Różnice w długości ciąży (normalny zakres: 37-42 tygodnie)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:431
msgid "Individual differences in fetal development"
msgstr "Indywidualne różnice w rozwoju płodu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Healthcare providers often use ultrasound measurements to refine the due "
"date, especially in early pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Pracownicy służby zdrowia często korzystają z pomiarów ultradźwiękowych w "
"celu ustalenia terminu porodu, szczególnie we wczesnej ciąży."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:446
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates. Only about 5%% of babies are born exactly on their "
"due date. Most babies are born within two weeks before or after the due "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Terminy płatności są szacunkowe. Tylko około 5%% dzieci rodzi się dokładnie "
"w wyznaczonym terminie. Większość dzieci rodzi się w ciągu dwóch tygodni "
"przed terminem porodu lub po nim."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is counted from the first day of your last menstrual period (LMP),"
" not from conception. This is why pregnancy is said to last 40 weeks even "
"though conception occurs about 2 weeks after LMP."
msgstr ""
"Ciążę liczy się od pierwszego dnia ostatniej miesiączki (LMP), a nie od "
"poczęcia. Dlatego mówi się, że ciąża trwa 40 tygodni, mimo że poczęcie "
"następuje około 2 tygodnie po LMP."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"If your cycle is longer or shorter than 28 days, adjust the cycle length in "
"the calculator for more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"Jeśli Twój cykl jest dłuższy lub krótszy niż 28 dni, dostosuj długość cyklu "
"w kalkulatorze, aby uzyskać dokładniejsze wyniki."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:560
msgid "Please enter a conception date."
msgstr "Proszę podać datę poczęcia."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:674
msgid "First Trimester End"
msgstr "Koniec pierwszego trymestru"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/due_date_calculator.html:676
msgid "Second Trimester End"
msgstr "Koniec drugiego trymestru"

